name: My creative process II
description:
I love color, I think and feel in colors but sometimes in black and white I find my zone of peace, of stillness, of expectation. 
"The dot is the basic graphic element and forms the minimum unit of visual communication, it can be intensified by means of color, size and its position on the plane. ... ... A line functions as a continuous succession of traced dots, as by a stroke or a dash." (Kandisky)
